'''sine'''

# (''trigonometry'') The ratio of the [[opposite leg]] to the [[hypotenuse]] of a [[right triangle]] with the given acute angle.
# (''mathematics'') The ''y'' coordinate of the point on the unit circle at the given counterclockwise angle from the ''x'' axis.
# (''mathematics'') The sum of the real or complex [[power series]]
::<math>\sum_1^\infty{{(-1)^{n-1}}\over{(2n-1)!}}x^{2n-1}</math>

